Professional Life:
Nathan spends his days immersed in his creative work, experimenting with various mediums and techniques to develop his artistic voice. He splits his time between working on personal projects, accepting commissioned pieces, and seeking out opportunities to showcase his art in local galleries or online platforms. While the financial challenges can be daunting, Nathan remains passionate and resilient in his pursuit of a career as a professional artist.

Personal Style:
